ckers\n- [Description] — waiting on [who/what]\n\n## Recent Activity\n- [Timesta
mp] [Action taken]\n```\n\n---\n\n## Priority System\n\nRefer to `../../company.
md` for the civilization-wide priority system. In general:\n\n1. **Founder messa
